description: Penthouse 1Bed +Office w/GARAGE PARKING at sought after PORT 45. This tastefully designed unit has a spacious/open floor plan w/ floor to ceiling windows, offering an abundance of natural light. The layout presents an oversized living room with access to a private balcony overlooking a manicured courtyard. The living room seamlessly opens to the sleek kitchen while offering space for a dining area. The designer kitchen is highlighted by a waterfall island, Bosch appliances, tile backsplash and combination of cabinetry & open shelving. Enter your king-size bedroom and find a custom walk-in closet that leads to the beautiful bathroom w/glass shower, Calcutta marble inspired tile, oversized vanity, medicine cabinet & linen storage. There is also a separate office ideal for work-from-home. Unit also offers high ceilings, hardwood floors, electronic blinds, in-unit laundry, & central AC. PORT 45 is pet-friendly, offers a concierge, gym, roof deck, clubroom, EV charging, & bike storage!
